    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero imperfections\u2014no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the original alloy wheels are free of any curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather upholstery shows no creasing or bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one. All onboard technology, from the high-fidelity sound system to the navigation and climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-book policy, supported by a comprehensive folder of every service record since new. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork, showing no signs of corrosion or fluid leaks. This is a rare, investment-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
