    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 997-generation Carrera S is a masterclass in analog precision. Powered by a 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, the power delivery remains exceptionally linear up to its 7,200 RPM redline. The M97 powerplant is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle with a factory short-shift kit, providing tactile engagement and precise gate selection. The chassis remains taut with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a limited-slip differential ensuring optimal lateral grip and corner-exit traction. This example is cosmetically flawless with original paint and a pristine undercarriage, showing no signs of thermal cycling wear or fluid seepage. Recent borescope inspection confirms zero cylinder scoring, and the IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a dual-row ceramic upgrade. A true enthusiast\u2019s specimen maintained to a concours standard.",
